<br /><br />

More info about URI DNSBL: <br />

<a href="http://www.surbl.org/">http://www.surbl.org/</a> <br />

<a href="http://dnsbl.invaluement.com/ivmuri/">http://dnsbl.invaluement.com/ivmuri/</a>',
